&lt;li&gt;Execute discussion guides, screeners, and research protocols as defined by the UX Lead.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Observe and document user behaviors, pain points, and patterns during sessions, distinguishing what users say from what they actually do or need.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Administer quantitative data collection methods (surveys, card sorting, tree testing) in support of research plans set by the UX Lead.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Compile and organize raw research data (notes, session artifacts) into clean, structured formats for UX lead to synthesize.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
